Update model input and output dimensions.

Args:
    shape_info (Dict[str, List[int | str]]): A dictionary of I/O names and
        their new shapes.

Example:

    openvino2onnx model.onnx -a reshape_model --config-file config.json

    # config.json:
    {
        "reshape_model:0": {
            "shape_info": {
                "input": [1, 2, 3, 4],
                "output": [4, 3, 2, 1]
            }
        }
    }
